::Battera:;

She fell to the floor clutching her throat with on hand.  She fell to 
her knees.  She was catching her breath and had tears running down 
her cheeks. "yes. I'm a pred. I'm here to talk to the Maximal leader 
about attending the peace conference." She was still on her knees, 
her face was red and her slender body trembled. These two could kill 
her and no one would stop them. She was fearing for her life.
